":cpp:enumerator:`LV_BUTTONMATRIX_CTRL_DISABLED` flag"
msgstr "I giorni del mese precedente e successivo hanno il flag :cpp:enumerator:`LV_BUTTONMATRIX_CTRL_DISABLED`"

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/widgets/calendar.rst:42
msgid ""
"today has a thicker border with the theme's primary color - highlighted "
"days have some opacity with the theme's primary color."
