#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/widgets/line.rst:10
msgid ""
"The Line Widget is capable of drawing straight lines between a set of "
"points."
msgstr "Il Widget \"Line\" è in grado di disegnare linee rette tra un insieme di punti."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/widgets/line.rst:18
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_PART_MAIN` uses the :ref:`typical background <typical"
