#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/widgets/scale.rst:97
msgid ""
"By default, the labels shown are the numeric values of the scale at the "
"major tick points.  Can you specify different label content by calling "
":cpp:expr:`lv_scale_set_text_src(scale, custom_labels)` where "
