"LV_ANIM_ON/OFF)`."
msgstr "La Tile View può scorrere fino a un tile specificato con :cpp:expr:`lv_tileview_set_tile(tileview, tile, LV_ANIM_ON/OFF)` o con :cpp:expr:`lv_tileview_set_tile_by_index(tileview, col_id, row_id, LV_ANIM_ON/OFF)`."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/widgets/tileview.rst:63
